>>>>>>>> Section 4, Level 1 is written for you. It explains exactly what 
>>>>>>>> your review covers, how to write your annotations in the Word 
>>>>>>>> document using the [IST ADD] and [IST CONFIRMED] tags, and what 
>>>>>>>> you must sign off before the FSD moves to TL-IST.
